oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: The Fighting 45th Infantry book
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: This book provides a history of the 45th Infantry Regiment during World War I. Images include portraits of commanding officers and training facilities and activities. The 45th Infantry Regiment was a regular army regiment which provided cadres for other formations throughout World War I. It also lists the names and units of the men who served in the 45th Infantry Regiment during World War I.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: World War, 1914-1918; World War, 1914-1918 - History
